metadata.name: Epamaker #1
metadata.description: Epamaker is an exclusive NFT collection for COS.TV, featuring 25 digital artworks of famous Brazilian Youtuber and COSer, Voepa. These digital artworks were designed by COS.TV original creator, Ilustrando Seu Dia, and represent the essense of Voepa and his community Owners receive exclusive benefits from Voepa and Contentos.
